    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-11-19T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-11-16T00:00:00-05:00" n="13"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d13">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">
                    <persName corresp="#p_WW1">Woodrow Wilson</persName> Papers</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The British Prime Minister</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_LGD1"
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Lloyd George</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to President <persName corresp="#p_WW1" type="to"
                            >Wilson</persName>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi>
                        </placeName> [<date
                            ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-content-and-sibling-dates"
                            calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1918-11-19T23:59:59-05:00"
                            notBefore="1918-11-16T00:00:00-05:00">undated</date>].<lb/>[Received
                        November 19, 1918.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>My heartiest thanks for your cordial and kindly message. I am certain that the
                    ideals of our two countries in regard to international reconstruction are
                    fundamentally the same and I feel sure that at the forthcoming peace conference
                    we shall be able to cooperate fruitfully to promote the reign of peace with
                    liberty and true democracy throughout the world.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_LGD1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">D. Lloyd George</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
